# ECP Specification Rules

- [ecp-overhaul.md](ecp-overhaul.md) is the implementation source of truth.
- Types live in `packages/types/src` (`@ecp/types`).
- Fluent API and runtime live in `packages/core/src` (`@ecp/core`).
- Workflow manifests use `schema: "@ecp.workflow"` and `version: "1.0"`.
- Workflows are portable; environments hold runtime/extension/policy bindings.
- Use Zod for config schemas and manifest validation where applicable.
- Do not reintroduce YAML `ECPContext` / `spec.yaml` without an explicit migration request.
